\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 21
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 How the faithful city has become a harlot! It was full of justice; Righteousness lodged in it, But now murderers. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 22
