\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 30
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 For you shall be as a terebinth whose leaf fades, And as a garden that has no water. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 31
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 The strong shall be as tinder, And the work of it as a spark; Both will burn together, And no one shall quench them. 
