\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 4
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 "I will give children to be their princes, And babes shall rule over them.\uc0\u8232 
\fs16 \cf2 \up13 5
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 The people will be oppressed, Every one by another and every one by his neighbor; 
\f0\fs24 \
